avdta.network.link.cell

Class SharedTransitCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • avdta.network.link.cell.Cell
      • avdta.network.link.cell.SharedTransitCell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Cell>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SharedTransitLinkCell, SharedTransitStartCell

    public abstract class SharedTransitCell
extends Cell
    This class represents a cell in the cell transmission model of a dynamic transit lane link (SharedTransitCTMLink). It stores Vehicles currently in the cell, and determines sending and receiving flows. This class is abstract; see SharedTransitLinkCell. Cells at the start and ends of links are slightly different; see SharedTransitStartCell and SharedTransitEndCell
